  "title": "Marketing Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Lead the planning and execution of end-to-end social media marketing strategies to support business and revenue objectives</p></li><li><p>Oversee content strategy and execution across platforms including Instagram, TikTok, Facebook and Xiaohongshu</p></li><li><p>Analyse social media performance metrics, generate insights and present regular reports to management</p></li><li><p>Manage and optimise paid social media advertising campaigns, including budget planning and ROI analysis</p></li><li><p>Ensure brand consistency across all social media channels and digital touchpoints</p></li><li><p>Coordinate and manage external partners such as creative agencies, influencers and media vendors</p></li><li><p>Stay informed on market trends, platform algorithm updates and competitive activities</p></li></ul><p><ul><li>Support overall digital marketing initiatives and campaign planning<br />Coordinate with internal teams and external partners such as designers, influencers, agencies and live stream vendors</li><li>Stay updated on social media, live commerce trends and platform algorithm changes</li><li>Host or co-host live streaming sessions when required to support marketing campaigns and product launches<br /></li></ul></p>",
